      "order": 1,
      "Description": "In today's marketplace, the term \"AI-powered\" appears on almost every new product and service, making it increasingly difficult to know what vendors actually mean when they use it. This lesson will help you cut through the noise by introducing practical frameworks for evaluating AI claims with confidence, even if you have no technical background. You will learn to ask the right questions, spot common marketing tactics, and identify the warning signs that suggest a claim may be exaggerated or misleading. By the end of the lesson, you will feel better equipped to assess whether a vendor's AI offering genuinely meets your needs or simply sounds impressive on paper.",
