          "number": 6,
          "slidetitle": "Red Flags to Watch For",
          "subtitle": "Warning signs that demand closer scrutiny",
          "slidecontent": "• \"100% accurate\" claims\n• No error rate disclosed\n• Vague phrases like \"intelligent\"\n• Zero real-world examples\n• No independent testing cited\n• Guaranteed results promised"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "slidetitle": "Spotting Red Flags in Claims",
          "subtitle": "Warning signs worth watching for",
          "slidecontent": "• Vague phrases like \"AI-powered\" or \"intelligent automation\" with no explanation of what the AI actually does\n\n• No mention of training data, accuracy rates, or known limitations\n\n• Promises of \"100% accuracy\" or \"fully autonomous\" decision-making\n\n• Case studies that show only cherry-picked results\n\n• Pressure to decide quickly, before you can ask deeper questions\n\n• No clear answer when you ask \"what happens when it gets it wrong\""
